                        <h3 id="section-reception-other" class="">其他招待方式</h3>
                        <ul id="2212febb-9950-8080-9077-f60a4e6d321a" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">安排高級餐廳用餐 - <mark class="highlight-red_background">歷屆主席、會長認餐</mark></li></ul>
                        <ul id="2212febb-9950-801d-8370-f91d89a13d7d" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">提供專車接送服務 - <mark class="highlight-red_background">遊覽車</mark></li></ul>
